1.title: Blood on the Forest Floor
1.plot: A Brazilian wandering spider tracks a hooded mantis; A land crab stumbles into a colony of army ants; A velvet worm meets a harvestman; A black jungle stalker spider encounters a black-faced katydid; A red Forest scorpion squares off against an amblypygid.

2.title: Utter Violence
2.plot: Violence erupts as a Giant Cockroach fights a Red-rump Tarantula; a Stripe-tailed Centipede targets a Vinegarroon, and an Orange Horned Katydid tackles a Banana Spider. A Golden Carpenter Ant tries to nail a Flag-tailed Assassin Bug.

3.title: Mother of All Wars
3.plot: A baby black-tailed scorpion that has been shaken off its mother's back encounters a pirate spider; A rock spider battles a lichen bark mantis; A candy cane katydid and a bug-eyed katydid collide; A spitting spider first encounters a black-tailed scorpion, then later a comb-footed spider; A tiger assassin bug gets trapped in a silver-back cross spider's web.

4.title: Murderous Intent
4.plot: A Leaf Cutter Ant faces a House Spider, a Costa Rican Cellar Spider fights a Geophilid Centipede, a Tiger Jumping Spider fights a Rainforest Jumping Spider, and a Katydid meets an Orange-mouth Tarantula. Then Dinosaur Ants battle a bunch of Trap Jaw Ants.

5.title: Deadly Duels
5.plot: A moss antis clashes with a tiger beetle; A horned katydid attacks an owl butterfly caterpillar; An army ant soldier strays too close to an ogre-faced spider's web; A red-thighed wandering spider stalks a black-tailed scorpion; A longicorn beetle flies into the web of a flame-bellied orb weaver.

6.title: Super Slayers
6.plot: A Leaf-tailed Mantis fights a Raspy Cricket and an armored Spiny Spider is ambushed by a Crab Spider. An underwater Mudeye duels with a Water Bug, then a Domino Beetle fights a Crimson-legged Assassin Bug while a Mangrove Tree Crab faces a Leopard Spider.

7.title: Monster Bug Wars Top 10

1.title: Death at Midnight
1.plot: A giant rain forest mantis and a spiny leaf insect; A bull and and a red-back spider; A water strider and a water spider; A white tail spider and a black house spider; A wolf spider and a Sydney funnel web spider.

2.title: Enemy Empire
2.plot: A tree scorpion gets too close to a green ant colony; A white tail spider and a cellar spider; A trap jaw ant and an ant lion; Two brown house spiders meet; A brown house spider meets a red-back spider; A desert centipede and a trapdoor spider.

3.title: The Quick and the Deadly
3.plot: An ogre-faced spider attacks an assassin bug; A bulldog raspy cricket faces off against a tarantula; A house centipede tracks a swift tree mantid; A marble scorpion encounters a colony of trap jaw ants; A metallic green jumping spider and a spitting spider stalk each other.

4.title: Shape Shifters
4.plot: A gray tree runner mantis meets a lichen huntsman; A katydid runs into upon a tent spider; A rhinoceros beetle stumbles into a colony of meat ants; A long-jawed jumping spider and a green jumping spider come face to face; A giant banded huntsman and a jungle huntsman meet up.

5.title: When Tribes Go to War
5.plot: It's a war when a Badge Huntsman Spider battles a Spider Hunting Scorpion, a Tree Centipede runs into a Balloon-Winged Katydid, and a Freshwater Crab meets a Tiger Leech. A Portia Spider battles a Long-Jawed Orb Weaver, and Paper Wasps take on Green Ants.

6.title: Rainforest Rampage
6.plot: A green-bellied huntsman attacks a colony of jumping jack ants; A green praying mantis and a katydid meet; A spiny tree cricket crosses paths with a golden orb weaver; A desert centipede hunts a desert scorpion; An earwig meets an assassin bug.

imdb.plot outline: Get a ringside seat for some of nature's deadliest encounters: losers aren't just KO'd, they're eaten alive. This is the no-holds-barred, real-life world of Spiders, Scorpions, Centipedes and Killer Ants who fight to the death. It's a bug-eat-bug gladiatorial contest where stings, spikes and deadly venom are wielded with cold-blooded precision.
